UID:v4LcbBHzEQpZMeJwOOvhL
SUMMARY:Beeswax Botanical Image Transfer
DTSTAMP:20260306T012148Z
DTSTART:20260317T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Taught by Ray Pfortner. In this hands-on workshop you learn eve
	rything you need to take your botanical art to the next level. Using 5″ x 
	7” photocopies of your own garden photos\, illustrations\, or journal page
	s\, you will learn how to transfer your image onto wood panels\, tiles\, o
	r stone using melted beeswax. You will bring your own photocopies\; all ad
	ditional equipment and materials will be provided. $31.50 BBGS Member/$45 
	Non-Member\n\nhttps://seatoday.6amcity.com/events/#/details/beeswax-botani
	cal-image-transfer/18185394/2026-03-17T00\n\nFrom SEAtoday - Arts & Cultur
